title: TutsPlus - Programming .NET
description: For over ten years, Microsoft's. NET Framework has been the platform to develop for if you want to target Windows or Windows-based technologies. Getting started with the. NET Framework can be a daunting task, as the. NET Framework class library is pretty darn big. But, thankfully, there are a core set of classes that you can use in any Windows or Web app. In this course, we'll take a look at these classes and how we can use them in our code.
